Reg Lewis (bodybuilder) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reg_Lewis_(bodybuilder) 0 Reg Lewis (born January 23, 1936 in Niles, California) is an American bodybuilder and actor. He worked with Mae West and appeared in a number of films including Sextette. Reg_Lewis ( born January_23_,_1936 in Niles , California ) is an_American_bodybuilder_and_actor .
